I don’t know how it got in his food, but I didn’t...

284
00:18:46,400 --> 00:18:47,200
Please calm down.

285
00:18:47,233 --> 00:18:49,020
Wait outside for the time being.

286
00:18:49,053 --> 00:18:50,220
Please.

