288
00:18:53,933 --> 00:18:55,326
The score is 12.

289
00:18:56,220 --> 00:18:57,366
Hey, take it easy for now.'

290
00:18:57,393 --> 00:18:58,220
He’s in good hands.

291
00:18:58,246 --> 00:18:59,246
