301
00:19:53,620 --> 00:19:54,953
What happened?

302
00:19:57,010 --> 00:19:58,010
It’s…

303
00:20:00,300 --> 00:20:02,300
Day’s big brother is in the hospital.

304
00:20:02,910 --> 00:20:04,186
Ozone?

305
00:20:05,220 --> 00:20:06,220
Yes.

306
00:20:08,870 --> 00:20:10,426
There was a razor blade in his food.

307
00:20:12,990 --> 00:20:13,940
What hospital?

308
00:20:13,966 --> 00:20:15,126
- Let’s go and see them.
- No.

309
00:20:15,550 --> 00:20:17,013
You stay home.

310
00:20:17,020 --> 00:20:18,546
Don’t go anywhere.

311
00:20:20,130 --> 00:20:21,140
Night.

312
00:20:21,180 --> 00:20:24,440
Maybe this has nothing to do with your birthday.

313
00:20:26,010 --> 00:20:28,513
But this was the food Day made for Ozone, Dream.

314
00:20:29,100 --> 00:20:31,193
You think he’d put the razor blade in it on purpose?

315
00:20:40,020 --> 00:20:41,580
What should we do?

316
00:20:45,886 --> 00:20:46,900
From now on,

317
00:20:48,410 --> 00:20:49,866
