318
00:20:50,370 --> 00:20:52,613
Stay where I can see you at all times.

319
00:20:53,040 --> 00:20:54,040
Understood?

320
00:21:02,480 --> 00:21:03,480
Okay.

321
00:21:03,690 --> 00:21:04,690
I understand.

322
00:21:18,540 --> 00:21:20,620
Are you Day, Ozone’s family?

323
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:21,633
Yes.

324
00:21:21,960 --> 00:21:22,960
That’s me.

325
00:21:23,200 --> 00:21:24,373
My name is Kung.

326
00:21:24,393 --> 00:21:25,700
I’m Night’s upperclassman.

327
00:21:25,706 --> 00:21:27,680
He told me you’re a friend.

328
00:21:28,510 --> 00:21:30,166
He asked me to take care of you.

329
00:21:30,186 --> 00:21:31,186
Okay.

330
00:21:33,520 --> 00:21:34,560
I must ask you,

331
00:21:34,586 --> 00:21:37,053
