332
00:21:37,420 --> 00:21:38,360
It’s at our house.

333
00:21:38,393 --> 00:21:39,513
On the dining table.

334
00:21:40,420 --> 00:21:42,020
You didn’t bring it with you, I take it.

335
00:21:42,280 --> 00:21:44,206
This is important,

336
00:21:44,220 --> 00:21:47,386
