337
00:21:47,406 --> 00:21:48,806
How exactly did it happen?

338
00:21:49,370 --> 00:21:50,680
It’s not rusted.

339
00:21:51,100 --> 00:21:53,840
I was making grilled pork noodles for Ozone.

340
00:21:53,873 --> 00:21:55,726
Everything looked fine.

341
00:21:55,746 --> 00:21:57,720
Ozone enjoyed it, like usual.

342
00:21:58,030 --> 00:22:01,513
