344
00:22:06,790 --> 00:22:08,853
He is safe now.

345
00:22:08,880 --> 00:22:10,973
The doctor is currently sewing him up.

346
00:22:11,320 --> 00:22:13,500
You can come in and see him if you want

347
00:22:13,526 --> 00:22:15,540
