359
00:22:45,030 --> 00:22:46,390
But this is part of the procedure.

360
00:22:46,780 --> 00:22:48,540
You only have to wait until tomorrow

361
00:22:48,566 --> 00:22:50,040
and Ozone will be home.

362
00:22:50,066 --> 00:22:51,066
Don’t worry.

363
00:23:25,880 --> 00:23:26,393
Night.

364
00:23:26,420 --> 00:23:27,873
He’s here.

365
00:23:39,570 --> 00:23:40,700
Win.

366
00:23:41,493 --> 00:23:43,490
You’re early to school.

367
00:23:43,770 --> 00:23:44,770
Dream.

368
00:23:45,453 --> 00:23:47,450
Can I sit with you for a bit?

369
00:23:47,473 --> 00:23:48,826
I’m supposed to meet my friends,

370
00:23:48,853 --> 00:23:50,546
