371
00:23:50,560 --> 00:23:51,406
Of course.

372
00:23:51,553 --> 00:23:52,553
Thank you.

373
00:24:09,600 --> 00:24:10,600
Dream.

374
00:24:10,860 --> 00:24:11,433
Yes?

375
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:13,820
