472
00:28:13,880 --> 00:28:15,100
Right?

473
00:28:15,126 --> 00:28:16,260
Yes.

474
00:28:18,780 --> 00:28:20,069
Careful not to hit the table, babe.

475
00:28:20,093 --> 00:28:21,340
Let’s go.

476
00:28:21,373 --> 00:28:23,080
Let’s grab some breakfast.

477
00:28:23,800 --> 00:28:25,253
What would you like today, babe?

478
00:28:25,273 --> 00:28:26,700
Is this a special occasion?

479
00:28:26,733 --> 00:28:28,062
Every day is a special occasion with you.

480
00:28:28,086 --> 00:28:29,300
I see.

481
00:28:32,920 --> 00:28:33,920
Night.

482
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:39,140
So now we know Professor Wiwat did kill a patient.

483
00:28:39,433 --> 00:28:41,140
On his birthday, no less.

484
00:28:41,840 --> 00:28:44,446
I just don’t know if it’s related.

485
00:28:45,790 --> 00:28:47,180
At this point,

486
00:28:47,226 --> 00:28:49,226
I don’t think there’s such a thing as coincidence.

487
00:28:50,000 --> 00:28:51,873
Both Day and I

488
00:28:51,906 --> 00:28:54,606
