525
00:30:28,120 --> 00:30:29,120
Hmm?

526
00:30:34,786 --> 00:30:37,653
I’ll wait just right outside, alright?

527
00:30:38,050 --> 00:30:38,786
Why?

528
00:30:38,800 --> 00:30:41,113
Not your fault.

529
00:30:41,980 --> 00:30:43,033
