541
00:31:34,520 --> 00:31:35,993
Never hurts me.

542
00:31:36,573 --> 00:31:38,086
Never ever.

543
00:31:49,260 --> 00:31:52,673
I… am here

544
00:31:52,706 --> 00:31:55,866
