555
00:32:36,166 --> 00:32:37,606
His food is so good.

556
00:32:39,513 --> 00:32:41,510
Day takes good care of me.

557
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:47,753
If… If I don’t have Day,

558
00:32:48,390 --> 00:32:50,193
I’ll be in trouble.

559
00:32:50,620 --> 00:32:51,886
I mean it.

560
00:33:10,540 --> 00:33:11,540
Day.

561
00:33:12,080 --> 00:33:13,326
All done.

562
00:33:15,560 --> 00:33:17,086
I want to go home.

563
00:33:17,106 --> 00:33:18,133
We will go home soon.

564
00:33:19,800 --> 00:33:21,473
Excuse us.

565
00:33:21,500 --> 00:33:22,553
